===Pronunciation===
בּית הכּרם / bêyth hak-kerem / bayth hak-keh'-rem

===Etymology===
From {{HH|1004}} and {{HH|3754}} with the article interposed; 

===Proper noun===
'''בּית הכּרם'''

# A house of the vineyard; Beth-hak-Kerem, a place in Palestine: - Beth-haccerem.

